<p>When most people hear "premium positioning," they think about price. About being expensive. About excluding people. This misunderstanding prevents more businesses from accessing premium positioning than any actual quality barrier — because premium is not fundamentally about price. Premium is about intentionality. And intentionality is available to any brand, at any stage.</p>
